# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:11
translate german jamiephone1_8f448c11:

    # "I feel my phone buzzing and pull it out of my pocket."
    "Ich spüre, wie mein Handy vibriert, und ziehe es aus der Tasche."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:13
translate german jamiephone1_9d0e5e2b:

    # "It's Jamie. I answer and lie down on the bed to talk."
    "Es ist Jamie. Ich nehme ab und lege mich aufs Bett, um zu reden."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:18
translate german jamiephone1_14dc4818:

    # pc "Hey"
    pc "Hey"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:20
translate german jamiephone1_e6b33c25:

    # gnd "Hey, [pcname]. How's it going?"
    gnd "Hey, [pcname]. Wie läuft’s?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:21
translate german jamiephone1_d57f9715:

    # pc "Pretty good, what's up?"
    pc "Ziemlich gut, was gibt’s?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:22
translate german jamiephone1_ab588a54:

    # gnd "Just felt like talking to you. You got some time?"
    gnd "Ich hatte einfach Lust, mit dir zu reden. Hast du Zeit?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:25
translate german jamiephone1_cf8b9e59:

    # pc "Sure, I got time."
    pc "Klar, ich hab Zeit."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:29
translate german jamiephone1_c2cf9bb6:

    # gnd "Wow, natural charmer aren't ya?"
    gnd "Wow, du bist ja ein geborener Charmeur, oder?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:30
translate german jamiephone1_80cdcc09:

    # pc "I like talking to you."
    pc "Ich rede gerne mit dir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:31
translate german jamiephone1_5d93fddb:

    # gnd "Good. I like talking to you too."
    gnd "Gut. Ich rede auch gerne mit dir."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:34
translate german jamiephone1_ca582ae4:

    # gnd "Oh, that's too bad. I'll talk to you some other time then."
    gnd "Oh, das ist schade. Dann reden wir ein anderes Mal."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:35
translate german jamiephone1_66ec96d3:

    # gnd "Sorry to bother you. Talk to you later."
    gnd "Entschuldige die Störung. Bis später."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:36
translate german jamiephone1_f01523d0:

    # "She hangs up the phone and I put it back into my pocket."
    "Sie legt auf und ich stecke das Handy wieder in die Tasche."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:42
translate german jamiephone1_62e5dd7e:

    # pc "So what's going on?"
    pc "Also, was ist los?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:44
translate german jamiephone1_d8868bcd:

    # gnd "Just been a rough week at school."
    gnd "Hatte einfach eine harte Woche in der Schule."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:45
translate german jamiephone1_d87c0f62:

    # pc "Really? You're usually so good at school. What are you struggling with?"
    pc "Wirklich? Du bist doch sonst so gut in der Schule. Womit hast du zu kämpfen?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:46
translate german jamiephone1_7e66235e:

    # gnd "I'm not really struggling with any of the schoolwork."
    gnd "Ich habe eigentlich keine Probleme mit den Schulaufgaben."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:47
translate german jamiephone1_43b9e385:

    # gnd "It's the in-class teaching program."
    gnd "Es ist das Unterrichtsprogramm in der Klasse."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:48
translate german jamiephone1_d6457b46:

    # gnd "I have to stand in front of all of these students and teach."
    gnd "Ich muss vor all diesen Schülern stehen und unterrichten."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:49
translate german jamiephone1_bc8e7906:

    # gnd "I'm just having a hard time standing at the front of the class with all of them looking at me."
    gnd "Es fällt mir einfach schwer, vorne in der Klasse zu stehen, während mich alle ansehen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:50
translate german jamiephone1_c80b503a:

    # pc "You're scared of public speaking?"
    pc "Hast du Angst vor öffentlichen Auftritten?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:51
translate german jamiephone1_15bcf641:

    # gnd "I guess so. I've never really had to do a lot of it. It's just uncomfortable having all eyes on me. It makes me really self-conscious."
    gnd "Ich glaube schon. Ich musste das bisher noch nicht oft machen. Es ist einfach unangenehm, wenn alle Augen auf mich gerichtet sind. Das macht mich total unsicher."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:54
translate german jamiephone1_1eff5d82:

    # gnd "I'm sure you're right, it's just hard right now."
    gnd "Da hast du sicher recht, es ist gerade einfach schwer."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:57
translate german jamiephone1_b138a837:

    # gnd "What do you mean?"
    gnd "Was meinst du damit?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:58
translate german jamiephone1_ecd76308:

    # pc "Well you're beautiful. I'm sure that guys stare at you all the time."
    pc "Na ja, du bist wunderschön. Ich bin mir sicher, dass die Jungs dich ständig anstarren."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:59
translate german jamiephone1_c31f5d75:

    # gnd "You think I'm beautiful?"
    gnd "Du findest mich schön?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:60
translate german jamiephone1_dd9bd446:

    # pc "Of course you are."
    pc "Natürlich bist du das."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:62
translate german jamiephone1_a5543b0a:

    # gnd "Thanks, [pcname]."
    gnd "Danke, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:63
translate german jamiephone1_92d2aff8:

    # gnd "But as nice as that is, it doesn't really help me with the public speaking."
    gnd "Aber so nett das auch ist, es hilft mir nicht wirklich beim Reden vor Publikum."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:66
translate german jamiephone1_9cc47622:

    # gnd "[pcname]!"
    gnd "[pcname]!"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:67
translate german jamiephone1_58f48bda:

    # gnd "I've heard of that method before, but in this case the audience is a bunch of thirteen-year-olds."
    gnd "Ich habe schon von dieser Methode gehört, aber in diesem Fall besteht das Publikum aus einem Haufen Dreizehnjähriger."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:68
translate german jamiephone1_84faa7b7:

    # pc "Oh right. Not a good idea then."
    pc "Ach so. Dann ist das wohl keine gute Idee."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:70
translate german jamiephone1_ba2f8001:

    # gnd "Right. Bad idea, try again."
    gnd "Stimmt. Schlechte Idee, versuch es noch mal."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:71
translate german jamiephone1_c0af307c:

    # pc "Maybe you could practice your lessons ahead of time on me?"
    pc "Vielleicht könntest du deine Unterrichtseinheiten vorher an mir üben?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:73
translate german jamiephone1_032af84e:

    # gnd "You'd do that for me?"
    gnd "Das würdest du für mich tun?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:74
translate german jamiephone1_2bf7afc7:

    # pc "Sure, just let me know and I'll listen to your lessons. Then during class, you can just pretend that you're giving your lessons to me again."
    pc "Klar, sag mir einfach Bescheid und ich höre mir deine Unterrichtseinheiten an. Dann kannst du im Unterricht einfach so tun, als würdest du mir die Unterrichtseinheiten noch einmal vortragen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:75
translate german jamiephone1_73d793ae:

    # pc "After a while, the butterflies will probably go away."
    pc "Nach einer Weile wird das Kribbeln im Bauch wahrscheinlich verschwinden."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:77
translate german jamiephone1_cadb83e9:

    # gnd "That's actually a pretty good idea."
    gnd "Das ist eigentlich eine ziemlich gute Idee."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:78
translate german jamiephone1_79c9211e:

    # pc "I have them occasionally."
    pc "Ich habe sie auch ab und zu."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:80
translate german jamiephone1_8dab1990:

    # gnd "Thanks, [pcname]. I'll let you know when I need you to listen to a lesson."
    gnd "Danke, [pcname]. Ich sag dir Bescheid, wenn du dir eine Lektion anhören sollst."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:81
translate german jamiephone1_050f909c:

    # pc "Sounds good."
    pc "Klingt gut."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:82
translate german jamiephone1_1bf27b6a:

    # gnd "Have you been doing okay in school?"
    gnd "Läuft es gut in der Schule?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:83
translate german jamiephone1_f033e017:

    # pc "It's been going okay so far."
    pc "Bis jetzt läuft es ganz gut."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:85
translate german jamiephone1_5e1eb57b:

    # gnd "Well if you need someone to study with, you can come hang out with me pretty much any weekday night while my dad's at work."
    gnd "Na ja, wenn du jemanden zum Lernen brauchst, kannst du fast jeden Abend unter der Woche bei mir vorbeikommen, solange mein Vater bei der Arbeit ist."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:86
translate german jamiephone1_b0435202:

    # pc "That sounds fun."
    pc "Das klingt lustig."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:87
translate german jamiephone1_d41eb353:

    # gnd "I don't know about fun. It's studying. But I'd be glad to help you."
    gnd "Ich weiß nicht, ob es Spaß macht. Es ist schließlich Lernen. Aber ich helfe dir gerne."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:88
translate german jamiephone1_57376a44:

    # pc "Thanks, Jamie, I'll probably take you up on that."
    pc "Danke, Jamie, das werde ich wahrscheinlich in Anspruch nehmen."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:89
translate german jamiephone1_6b6bc48a:

    # gnd "I hope so."
    gnd "Das hoffe ich."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:91
translate german jamiephone1_1b403d26:

    # gnd "Alright, [pcname], thanks for listening. It's getting pretty late, I better go to bed."
    gnd "Okay, [pcname], danke fürs Zuhören. Es wird schon ziemlich spät, ich gehe besser ins Bett."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:92
translate german jamiephone1_fb7cffd0:

    # pc "Okay, good night."
    pc "Okay, gute Nacht."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:93
translate german jamiephone1_e206e304:

    # gnd "Night, [pcname]."
    gnd "Gute Nacht, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamiePhone/jamiephone1.rpy:95
translate german jamiephone1_6865bc2c:

    # "She hangs up and I put the phone on my nightstand. She's right, it is getting pretty late. Better get ready for bed."
    "Sie legt auf und ich lege das Telefon auf meinen Nachttisch. Sie hat recht, es wird schon ziemlich spät. Ich mache mich besser bettfertig."

